    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>As a prospective parent (hopefully in a couple of years!), it is awfully nice to read the perspective of a parent who doesn&#39;t have a big, complicated, and unanswerable Philosophy about feeding their child. The obsessive number of rules that I see many parents follow have intimidated me in the past, and I am glad that they are not necessary for producing a happy and healthy kid. </p>
