  <li id="comment-41001" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Amy</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/01/in-it-together/#comment-41001"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-01-16T18:07:00-05:00">Thursday, January 16, 2014 at 6:07 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>After raising two fairly picky eaters I recently said to some new moms, &#8220;If I had it to do over I would cook healthy foods, put everything on the table and not say a word. No &#39;just 2 more bites&#39; or &#39;eat this and then you can have dessert&#39; or &#39;pleeeease, just eat!&#8221; The moms all looked at me like I had two heads. Your post perfectly capsulized my feelings on the matter. As always, brilliantly, supportively, humorously put. And that little girl of yours in precious!</p>
    </div>

