  <li id="comment-41028" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/02929727558577488718" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">nanne</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/01/in-it-together/#comment-41028"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-01-16T22:11:17-05:00">Thursday, January 16, 2014 at 10:11 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
