    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is incredible. Molly, I hope you realize how incredibly fortunate you are that your daughter has such a flexible palate at such a young age. We &#8220;feed&#8221; our 3 year old son that which we&#39;re eating, and it is very touch and go. He loves flavor and spice, yet hates texture and has developed a lot of irrational food fears. Keep doing what you are doing! Hopefully her &#8220;picky switch&#8221; will remain off!</p>
    </div>

